### 8.3 Post in Community

**Endpoint:** `POST /api/v1/communities/{id}/posts`

| Parameter | In   | Type | Description                        |
| --------- | ---- | ---- | ---------------------------------- |
| [id](file:///c:/Users/yamit/Downloads/Desktop/livanaFinalbackend/backend-services/src/handlers/listing.rs#301-372)      | path | UUID | ID of the community to post in     |

**Headers:**

```
Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>
Content-Type: application/json
```

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "content": "Has anyone noticed the recent price trends in Bandra? Seems like a good time to invest!"
}
```

| Field     | Type   | Required | Description         |
| --------- | ------ | -------- | ------------------- |
| `content` | string | Yes      | Content of the post |

**Success Response** `201 Created`:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Post created successfully",
  "data": {
    "post_id": "d3e4f5a6-7b8c-4d9e-0f1a-2b3c4d5e6f7a",
    "community_id": "f7a8b9c0-1d2e-4f3a-b5c6-7d8e9f0a1b2c",
    "author_id": "c4d5e6f7-8a9b-4c0d-1e2f-3a4b5c6d7e8f",
    "content": "Has anyone noticed the recent price trends in Bandra? Seems like a good time to invest!",
    "created_at": "2026-03-07T19:15:00Z"
  }
}
```

> **Security:** Only members of the community can create posts. Non-members receive `403 Forbidden`.

